steps.prompt:
Create an agent-ready UI description from this capture context.

Memo title: {{TITLE}}
Memo transcript or note:
{{TRANSCRIPT}}

Screenshot count: {{SCREENSHOT_COUNT}}
Screenshot context:
{{SCREENSHOT_CONTEXT}}

VLM screenshot description:
{{SCREENSHOT_VISION}}

Visible OCR text:
{{SCREENSHOT_OCR}}

Return exactly these sections:

Current UI
- Identify the app, screen, visible task, and dominant content.

Interactive Controls
- List visible controls, labels, selected states, disabled states, and where they are on screen.

State And Constraints
- Note errors, loading states, missing data, modal sheets, scroll position, and anything that limits the next action.

Suggested Agent Context
- Write a concise paragraph that can be pasted into another AI agent so it understands this UI and what the user likely needs next.
